text: The Darling Buds of May is an English comedy drama television series. It was produced by Yorkshire Television & channelled and networked by ITV from 7 April 1991 to 4 April 1993. It stars Pam Ferris, David Jason, Catherine Zeta- Jones, Philip Franks, Rachel Bell, Moray Watson, Kika Mirvlees & Susie Blake.
